("Hex2Rgb","public class ColorUtils { public static int[] hexToRgb(String h){h=h.replace(\"#\",\"\");return new int[]{Integer.parseInt(h.substring(0,2),16),Integer.parseInt(h.substring(2,4),16),Integer.parseInt(h.substring(4,6),16)};} }","assertArrayEquals(new int[]{255,0,0},ColorUtils.hexToRgb(\"#FF0000\"))"),
