("FactIter","public class MathUtils { public static long factIter(int n){if(n<0)throw new IllegalArgumentException();long r=1;for(int i=2;i<=n;i++)r*=i;return r;} }","assertEquals(1,MathUtils.factIter(0))\nassertEquals(120,MathUtils.factIter(5))"),
